spec_data.Name: texlive-wrapfig
spec_data.Description:
Allows figures or tables to have text wrapped around them. Does
not work in combination with list environments, but can be used
in a parbox or minipage, and in twocolumn format. Supports the
float package.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:21:46 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Produces figures which text can flow around
